calls etc.

This transaction needs absolute secrecy,to avoid any breach of Law. If you are not the intended beneficiary of this fund, please treat as
urgent a reply as to whom you are intending to forward to the account for subsequent sharing and transfer.

Thank you and God bless you.

Yours truly,
Rosa Abo
